<!DOCTYPE concept PUBLIC "-//OASIS//DTD DITA Concept//EN" "concept.dtd">
<concept outputclass="docs one-sidebar sidebar-first" id="registering_ha">
 <title>Registering Eucalyptus: HA</title>
 <shortdesc></shortdesc>
 <conbody>
 	<p>Component registration for HA Eucalyptus is more complex than for non-HA Eucalyptus because the components (except for NCs) occur in separated pairs. You must perform the registration tasks for each paired machine. </p>
 		 <note type="important">Make sure that you have run euca_conf --initialize on exactly one host: the
 		 	primary CLC.</note>
 	
 	<table>
 		<title>Eucalyptus HA Registration Process</title>
 		<tgroup cols="2">
 			<tbody>
 				<row>
 					<entry>1</entry>
 					<entry>Register the secondary CLC</entry>
 				</row>
 				<row>
 					<entry>2</entry>
 					<entry>Register the Walrus pairs</entry>
 				</row>
 				<row>
 					<entry>3</entry>
 					<entry>Register the CCs</entry>
 				</row>
 				<row>
 					<entry>4</entry>
 					<entry>Register the VMware Broker</entry>
 				</row>
 				<row>
 					<entry>5</entry>
 					<entry>Register the SCs</entry>
 				</row>
 				<row>
 					<entry>6</entry>
 					<entry>Register the NCs</entry>
 				</row>
 			</tbody>
 		</tgroup>
 	</table>
 	
 </conbody>
</concept>
